settings.description:
A familiar setting based on NSMB 1-1

--Intended with any character--
Things get mysterious at night. Use pullied platforms and pipes to traverse piranhas and hot heads.
Penguins Afoot! Beware of the vicious creatures as you travel through this worn landscape!
Your spaceship is breaking apart and has been overrun by some kinds of creatures,the only other base not overrun is on the moon.Take you medical mushroom and run.

First level! This is the first of what will be a 72 (plus 1 extra for those who complete all 72 levels 100%!) level series! This will take a while! Good luck getting all 360 Ace coins!
Difficulty: 3/5
Decided to make this cause why not

Trek around this shifting environment as you go through doors! 

--Intended with any character--

Solve puzzles, fill in empty spaces, set record time .. and play sudoku. Except it isn't sudoku? I'm baffled at what it's called. 

Hint: Make sure not to have a starman while getting a goomba's shoe.
I wanted to do a very complete level 0-0

Special levels I created for my fiance, enjoy. <3

A remake of Super Mario World 1-1. Somehow, Rexes are now red and hopping. Banzai Bills are now smaller and homes in to you.
